.TH SINGINE-JDBC-URL 1 "2026-03-13" "singine 0.2.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
singine-jdbc-url \- print the JDBC URL for a Singine SQLite bridge database
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B singine jdbc-url
[\fB--db\fR \fIPATH\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Prints the
.B jdbc:sqlite:
URL corresponding to the selected bridge database path.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B --db \fIPATH\fR
SQLite database path. Default is
.IR /tmp/sqlite.db .
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
singine jdbc-url
singine jdbc-url --db /tmp/sqlite.db
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR singine (1),
.BR singine-bridge (1)
